{"tid":1630154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電台記者被汽油彈擲中　燒近耳朵須送院","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:43:01.000Z","uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f52a570eabfd0bb6697b4f4e12ac114ad56e39c","tid":1630154,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484617-20191006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484617-20191006.htm&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6vzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=3495b669\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484617-20191006.htm&h=156461ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484617-20191006.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大批防暴警察下午5時許在灣仔軒尼詩道近天樂里驅散示威者，沿途施放催淚彈，有示威者向警方的方向投擲汽油彈，現場一名身穿記者採訪背心的人士，一度被擲中，身上的膠雨衣著火，有身穿黑衣示威者上前為他撲熄火種。<br />\n<br />\n本台證實，被擲中的是本台電視部一名記者。有片段拍攝到當時他身穿的雨衣著火，燒近耳朵位置，目前他已送往律敦治醫院治理。"},{"pid":"e0ae6dab14d046bf83453859b80f2c3dc78bd1f0","tid":1630154,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"now定rthk ?"},{"pid":"cb886e1af27efe7d6ae65e68870ca22c395504ee","tid":1630154,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0ae6dab14d046bf83453859b80f2c3dc78bd1f0","tid":1630154,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"now定rthk ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"rthk"},{"pid":"396f15841114580a7623784344754ff985e373fd","tid":1630154,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:38:56.000Z","msg":"rthk"},{"pid":"18ccab081063f8ed6785ef33ba0418aa56c177aa","tid":1630154,"uid":115170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:39:08.000Z","msg":"一日兩單咁奇怪? 會唔會有鬼特登擲記者呀"},{"pid":"d5de9deb10b7d33fce2ecf47ef6322ba